rows.label: qst201822_msg0001
rows.name: So they wouldn't listen to you?

rows.label: qst201822_msg0002
rows.name:
No, they wouldn't give
me the time of day.

rows.label: qst201822_msg0003
rows.name: Hmm, so you got turned away...

rows.label: qst201822_msg0004
rows.name: Many of us Phonexes are very cautious.

rows.label: qst201822_msg0005
rows.name:
We don't easily trust outsiders.
Especially humans, since many
of them are nasty.

rows.label: qst201822_msg0006
rows.name:
I see... So even I can't
earn their trust...

rows.label: qst201822_msg0007
rows.name:
Don't be so down. It'll be fine
if you bring them some food.

rows.label: qst201822_msg0009
rows.name:
So if you give them that, I'm sure
they'll cheer up and talk to you.

rows.label: qst201822_msg0010
rows.name: I see, food! That's a good idea!

rows.label: qst201822_msg0012
rows.name:
Come on, everyone! Let's
go find the Phonexes'
favorite food right away!
